description: SearchGUI is a user-friendly open-source graphical user interface for configuring and running proteomics identification search engines, currently supporting X!Tandem, MS-GF+, MetaMorpheus, MS Amanda, MyriMatch, Comet, Tide, Andromeda and OMSSA.
name: searchgui
